cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL

The paper deals with indoor scene synthesis, which involves generating 3D layouts of indoor environments. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR) domains. The paper also uses machine learning techniques to learn priors from data, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) domains. Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques to extract priors, which falls under the computational linguistics (cs.CL) domain.
